HOME.FirstScreen.script.message: Oomol Studio makes it easy to connect code snippets and API services through intuitive visual interactions

HOME.BrandAssets.description-1.message: All OOMOL trademarks, logos, or other brand elements can never be modified or used for

HOME.BrandAssets.description-2.message: any other purpose other than to represent OOMOL Inc.

HOME.BrandAssets.scripts-1.message: Download OOMOL official logos, including as SVG's, in both light and dark theme.

HOME.BrandAssets.scripts-2.message: Do not use any other color for the word mark.

HOME.Scenes.subtitle.message: OOMOL enables flexible construction of structured and unstructured data workflows through free node combination.

HOME.Scenes.data-science.inner.message: OOMOL natively supports Python/JS for data processing and chart generation, featuring built-in AI function nodes and large model APIs for creating modern AI analytics workflows.

HOME.Scenes.media-processing.inner.message: OOMOL allows developers to create customizable video processing nodes, enabling content creators to automate tasks like multilingual subtitling through drag-and-drop workflows.

HOME.Features.subtitle.message: Easy drag-and-drop workflows, professional code editor, and elegant data visualization.

HOME.Features.intuitive-interaction.inne.message: Easily build workflows, flexibly configure nodes, and preview data.

HOME.Features.pre-installed-environment..message: Built-in Python & Node.js, VSCode-based with AI and clear logs.

HOME.Features.programming-friendly.inner.message: No installation needed; OOMOL uses containers for seamless workflow sharing.

HOME.Features.support-sharing.inner.message: Publish as source code for easy secondary development by others.

HOME.Features.block-sharing.inner.message: Publish as a block for easy use by others, like the npm community.

HOME.Guide.subtitle.message: Explore the Community to find a workflow that fits your needs.

HOME.Guide.project-10.description.message: Various feature sets of the SiliconFlow platform

HOME.Built-in.subtitle.message: Built-in LLM blocks for improved AI workflow efficiency.

HOME.GetStartedPrompt.subtitle.message: Oomol Studio makes it easy to build workflows by visually connecting code and APIs.

FEATURES.title.message: All the features that you need

FEATURES.description.message: Easy drag-and-drop workflows, professional code editor, and elegant data visualization.

FEATURES.sceneOne.content-1.message: Build workflows with simple drag-and-drop Blocks to fit your needs.

FEATURES.sceneOne.content-2.message: Automatically offer UI components based on parameter types for easier use.

FEATURES.sceneOne.content-3.message: An intuitive UI helps users clearly understand the system’s status.

FEATURES.sceneOne.content-4.message: Readable logs with clear sequence and explicit status.

FEATURES.sceneTwo.content-5.message: Built-in Python and Node.js with support for open-source library installation.

FEATURES.sceneTwo.content-6.message: Based on Visual Studio Code with code completion, highlighting, and AI tips.

FEATURES.sceneTwo.content-7.message: Each node is a function—customize them easily if you know programming.

FEATURES.block-1.title.message: Containerized development environment for seamless cross-system workflow sharing.

FEATURES.block-2.title.message: Protect local environment and data security through secure isolation.

FEATURES.block-3.title.message: Unified Linux environment, easy image deployment to cloud.

FEATURES.block-4.title.message: Share workflow templates for easy scenario application and secondary development.

FEATURES.block-5.title.message: Share Block library with connectable, ready-to-use functions.

FEATURES.block-6.title.message: Code synced to GitHub for collaborative development and upkeep.
